\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Subsubsection*
Separating Equilibrium
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Let 
\begin_inset Formula $k=\frac{3}{2}$
\end_inset

.
 We are looking for an equilibrium that consists of:
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
Agents with 
\begin_inset Formula $a_{H}$
\end_inset

